---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="About Mariana Costa, data engineer and open-source contributor.">
  <div class="about-page">
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-avatar">
        <img src="/img/profile.jpg" alt="Mariana Costa" width="88" height="88" />
      </div>
      <h1>Mariana Costa</h1>
      <p class="about-bio">💻</p>
      <div class="about-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/mrncstt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrncstt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="about-body">
    <section class="about-section">
      <h2 data-lang="en">What I do</h2>
      <h2 data-lang="pt">O que eu faço</h2>
      <h2 data-lang="es">Lo que hago</h2>
      <p data-lang="en">
        I build and maintain data pipelines. My main stack is PySpark, Databricks,
        Terraform, and Git. Outside work I contribute to open-source projects, experiment
        with data visualization, and write about what I learn along the way.
      </p>
      <p data-lang="pt">
        Construo e mantenho pipelines de dados. Minha stack principal é PySpark, Databricks,
        Terraform e Git. Fora do trabalho contribuo com projetos open-source, experimento
        com visualização de dados e escrevo sobre o que aprendo pelo caminho.
      </p>
      <p data-lang="es">
        Construyo y mantengo pipelines de datos. Mi stack principal es PySpark, Databricks,
        Terraform y Git. Fuera del trabajo contribuyo a proyectos open-source, experimento
        con visualización de datos y escribo sobre lo que aprendo en el camino.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2 data-lang="en">This blog</h2>
      <h2 data-lang="pt">Este blog</h2>
      <h2 data-lang="es">Este blog</h2>
      <p data-lang="en">
        I write a mix of technical posts, short TIL notes, and miscellaneous things.
        I publish in English, Spanish and Portuguese depending on the topic and audience.
        I share things I've actually built, broken, or tried to figure out.
      </p>
      <p data-lang="pt">
        Escrevo uma mistura de posts técnicos, notas curtas de TIL e coisas variadas.
        Publico em inglês, espanhol e português dependendo do tema e do público.
        Compartilho coisas que realmente construí, quebrei ou tentei entender.
      </p>
      <p data-lang="es">
        Escribo una mezcla de posts técnicos, notas cortas de TIL y cosas variadas.
        Publico en inglés, español y portugués según el tema y la audiencia.
        Comparto cosas que realmente construí, rompí o intenté entender.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2 data-lang="en">Elsewhere</h2>
      <h2 data-lang="pt">Onde mais</h2>
      <h2 data-lang="es">En otros sitios</h2>
      <p data-lang="en">
        I keep my code on <a href="https://github.com/mrncstt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        and connect with people on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrncstt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
        My favorite card in Risk is "conquering 24 territories of my choice".
      </p>
      <p data-lang="pt">
        Mantenho meu código no <a href="https://github.com/mrncstt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        e me conecto com pessoas no <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrncstt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
        Minha carta favorita no War é "conquistar 24 territórios à sua escolha".
      </p>
      <p data-lang="es">
        Mantengo mi código en <a href="https://github.com/mrncstt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        y me conecto con personas en <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrncstt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
        Mi carta favorita en Risk es "conquistar 24 territorios a tu elección".
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="about-disclaimer" data-lang="en">
      All opinions are my own.
    </p>
    <p class="about-disclaimer" data-lang="pt">
      Todas as opiniões são minhas.
    </p>
    <p class="about-disclaimer" data-lang="es">
      Todas las opiniones son mías.
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
